<p>I am using Chrome on Mac and have been manually numbering lists of items because I am struggling to get the rich text formatting work. However I was ashamed today to find someone has had to go through and fix all my answers.</p>

<p>Is there a trick to it? How to get auto numbering. When I try I get this:</p>

<ol>
